{"questionId":"22002244","questionHtml":"<p>The coefficient of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>6</mn></msup></math> in the expansion of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>8</mn></msup></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>448</mn></math>.</p>\n<p>The coefficient of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>6</mn></msup></math>&nbsp;in the expansion of&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mo>+</mo><mi>b</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>10</mn></msup></math> is <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2880</mn></math>.</p>\n<p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math> and the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math>, where <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo> </mo><mo>,</mo><mo> </mo><mi>b</mi><mo>&gt;</mo><mn>0</mn></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>product of a binomial coefficient, a power of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><msup><mi>x</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></math> and a power of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi></math> seen&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>evidence of correct term chosen</p>\n<p>for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn></math>&nbsp;:&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp;(or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn></math>)&nbsp; OR&nbsp; for <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>10</mn></math> : <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math> (or <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>r</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p>correct equations (may include powers of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math>)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mmultiscripts><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn><mprescripts></mprescripts><mn>8</mn></mmultiscripts><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>6</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>448</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>28</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>6</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>448</mn><mo>⇒</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>6</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>16</mn><mo>)</mo></math>,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mmultiscripts><mi>C</mi><mn>2</mn><mprescripts></mprescripts><mn>10</mn></mmultiscripts><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2880</mn><mo>&nbsp;</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>45</mn><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>2880</mn><mo>⇒</mo><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup><msup><mi>b</mi><mn>8</mn></msup><mo>=</mo><mn>64</mn><mo>)</mo></math></p>\n<p>attempt to solve their system in a and b algebraically or graphically&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp;;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:&nbsp;</strong>Award a maximum of&nbsp;<em><strong>(M1)(A1)A1A1(M1)A1A0</strong></em>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp;and/or&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>±</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[7 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"22002244","referenceCode":"23M.2.SL.TZ1.6","subjectId":"50-dp-mathematics-analysis-and-approaches","title":"The coefficient of x6 in the expansion of (ax3+b)8 is 448. The coefficient of x6 in the expansion of (ax3+b)10 is 2880. Find the value of a and the value of b, where a , b>0.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"6","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 7]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.9—Binomial theorem where n is an integer"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}